caption.text:
Happy Dragon Quest XI S Echoes of an Elusive Age Definitive Edition launch day! 🐲🐉🔥🎮🕹⛩⛺⛲🏯🏰
-
I was supposed to receive it on launch day, but damn whoever invested new public holiday onto AFL Grand Final Friday = no delivery process until Mad Monday! Okay. I've played demo on Nintendo Switch. Took 10 hours. Longest demo length ever I think so! MASTERPIECE in every way! PERFECT JRPG game for me! GOTY 2019 worthy easily. Oh alongside with Kingdom Hearts III!
-
DQ XI reminds me of Dragon Quest VIII PS2 game, last DQ game on console then all DQ games on handheld platforms to DQ XI on PS4, a year later on Nintendo Switch with extra contents! Oops I haven't started PS4 version yet. I guess I'll go on Nintendo Switch version with carryover save data from demo.
-
September 2019 the PACKED gaming expensive month is... OVER! "YAY!" My little wallet says.
-
